
    +-----------------------------------------+------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
    | Login                                   | post login body:{email}, {pw}                                                |
    +-----------------------------------------+------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
    | Register                                | post register body:{pw}, {email}                                             |
    |                                         +------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
    |                                         | put register body:{token}                                                    |
    +-----------------------------------------+------------------------------------------------------------------------------+

    +-----------------------------------------+------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
    | Search                                  | get docents                                                                  |
    +-----------------------------------------+------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
    | Appointments/Informationen von Dozent   | get docents/{docent_id}                                                       |
    +-----------------------------------------+------------------------------------------------------------------------------+

    +-----------------------------------------+------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
    | in Appointment einschreiben (Studenten) | ! post {user_id}/appointment_request body:{appointment_id}, {time}, ...      |
    +-----------------------------------------+------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
    | Appointment annehmen/ablehnen           | ! put {docent_id}/appointment_request body:{id}, {state}                     |
    |                                         +------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
    |                                         | ! delete {user_id}/appointment_request/{id}                                  |
    +-----------------------------------------+------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
    | Appointments des Users                  | ! get {user_id}/appointment                                                  |
    |                                         +------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
    |                                         | ! get {user_id}/appointment/{count}                                          |
    |                                         +------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
    |                                         | ! get {user_id}/appointment/{from}/{to}                                      |
    |                                         +------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
    |                                         | ! post {docent_id}/appointment body:{day}, {time}, {description}             |
    |                                         +------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
    |                                         | ! delete {docent_id}/appointment/{appointment_id}                            |
    +-----------------------------------------+------------------------------------------------------------------------------+


    +-----------------------------------------+------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
    | Settings                                | ! get {user id}/settings                                                     |
    |                                         +------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
    |                                         | ! put {user_id}/settings body:{faculties}, {pw}, {email}                     |
    +-----------------------------------------+------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
    | Ban user                                | ! get {docent_id}/banned_users                                               |
    |                                         +------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
    |                                         | ! post {docent_id}/baned_user body:{user_id}                                 |
    |                                         +------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
    |                                         | ! delete {docent_id}/banned_users/{user_id}                                  |
    +-----------------------------------------+------------------------------------------------------------------------------+


